text: Lisette Tammik (born 14 October 1998) is an Estonian footballer who plays as a forward for Spanish Primera División club Santa Teresa CD and the Estonia women's national team. ==Career== Tammik has been capped for the Estonia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==Honours== Flora *Naiste Meistriliiga: 2018 *Estonian Women's Supercup: 2018 Napoli *Serie B: 2019–20 *Serie C: 2018–19 ==References== ==External links== * * * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Tallinn Category:Estonian women's footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Estonia women's international footballers Category:Estonian expatriate footballers Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Italy Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Italy Category:Expatriate sportspeople in Spain
